pr_title: Support JSON as on-disk format for histograms
pr_body:
This adds support for JSON as an on-disk format for histograms as described in [MDEV-21130](https://jira.mariadb.org/browse/MDEV-21130).

At the moment, JSON histograms can now be enabled with: `set histogram_type=JSON;` and running `ANALYZE TABLE` as usual.

Some improvements over the existing histogram format is also tracked at [MDEV-26125](https://jira.mariadb.org/browse/MDEV-26125).

Signed-off-by: Michael Okoko <okokomichaels@outlook.com>
